The Immortal Zhen Yuan Captures the Pilgrim Priest Monkey Makes Havoc in the Wuzhuang Temple The meal is cooked the three disciples said as they entered the hall what did you call us for I'm not asking about the meal disciples said Sanzang This temple has things called manfruit or something that look like babies
