Brother he said trying to hurry Monkey up the master is waiting for us
He wants us back as soon as possible Come and look round the Water Curtain Cave was Monkey's reply
It's very good of you to offer said Pig but I mustn't keep the master waiting so I'm afraid I can't visit the cave Then I won't waste your time said Monkey
