Journey to the West If you don't know how he was dealt with or whether he survived listen to the explanation in the next installment
Pig Moves the Monkey King Through His Goodness Sun the Novice Subdues the Ogre Through Cunning They swore to become brothers And the dharma brought them back to their true nature
When metal and Wood were tamed the True Result could be achieved The MindApe and the Mother of Wood combined to make the elixir
