You would have to go into these mountains said Monkey to find out how many monsters there are and all about the mountains and what the monsters' caves are like so that we can go across it Nothing to it replied Pig
I'll patrol the mountains The idiot hitched up his tunic grasped his rake and proudly struck deep into the mountains
His spirits were high as he hurried along the path
Monkey could not hold back an unkind laugh
Wretched ape said Sanzang you haven't a shred of affection for your brothers only jealousy
