In this Flattop Mountain there was a Lotus Flower Cave where there dwelt two fiends the Senior King Gold Horn and the Junior King Silver Horn
Gold Horn sat in his chair of office and said to Silver Horn It's a long time since we patrolled the mountain A fortnight replied Silver Horn
