It's just that the wind has changed Never you mind about whether the wind has changed or not said Monkey
Keep moving From then on they all stopped talking and wished they could step over the mountain with a single stride
The story switches back to the evil spirit whose three or four shouts had found no response
I've been waiting for the Tang Priest here he thought and I saw that he was only about a mile away I wonder why he's still not here after all this time
He must have taken a short cut He then braced himself slipped out of his bonds and went up into the air again in his red light to take another look
