We two are his favorite disciples Besides our masters are such lovers of the Way and its followers that they only need to hear the word 'Way' to come right outside to welcome a visitor For us to take you in there would be as easy as blowing away ashes Monkey chanted a deep and respectful reeer and then said I would be very grateful for an introduction
Let's go in Wait a moment said the Taoist
