When the Buddhist monks faraway on the strand saw Monkey kill the two Taoists they abandoned their cart and came running over saying This is awful this is awful You've killed the king's relations Who are the king's relations Monkey asked
The monks fenced him in with their earthmoving baskets and said Their masters don't have to greet the king when they enter the throne hall or take leave of him when they go The king addresses them as 'Elder Brother Teacher'
